T1  - Portfolio turnpike theorems for constant policies
AU  - Ross, Stephen A.
JO  - Journal of Financial Economics
VL  - 1
IS  - 2
SP  - 171
EP  - 198
PY  - 1974
DA  - 1974/07/01/
